                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Ezio turns into a cloud of vapor, as the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vapor Form] spell, or back to its normal form. Ezio loses fast healing while in gaseous form.</p>\n<p>Ezio can remain in this form indefinitely.</p>"
